HEADWORD: Apollinaris water
<hw>A*pol`li*na"ris wa"ter</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>An effervescing
alkaline mineral water used as a table beverage. It is obtained from a
spring in Apollinarisburg, near Bonn.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Apollo</ent>⟦br⟧
